TestOOB - Testing Out Of (The) Box

===========================================================================
= Description:
===========================================================================

TestOOB is a bundle of extensions to Python's built-in unit
testing framework (module unittest).

===========================================================================
= Features:
===========================================================================

- Easy to use, simply replace unittest.main() with testoob.main()!
- Extensible filtering (see testoob/extractors.py)
- Advanced reporting   (see testoob/reporting.py)
- Extra testing facilities

See the sources for more details.

===========================================================================
= Installation:
===========================================================================

See file INSTALL

